        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 25. Geographical distribution of four known Liogenys species occurring in the Chacoan province and its boundaries. Shaped points: previously known species; colors: Neotropical provinces (Morrone 2014) and Monte province from the South American Transition Zone (Roig-Juñent et al. 2018)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4561328/files/figure.png" .

