        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 17. Liogenys pallens Blanchard, 1851 male lectotype: A) dorsal, D) labels, G) lateral, H) pygidium, and parameres: I) dorsal, J) lateral. Liogenys fulvescens Blanchard, 1851 female lectotype: B) dorsal, E) labels. Liogenys flavicollis Frey, 1964 female holotype: C) dorsal, F) labels." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4561312/files/figure.png" .

